short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hide specified emotes when you are playing duels in GeoGuessr.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is for GeoGuessr https://www.geoguessr.com/
It enables you to hide specified emotes when you play duels.

https://posio.pages.dev/

https://github.com/anofficialposio/geoguessr-mute-emotes
